gomodel:SYNGO_1065  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Data in Figure 7 shows live cell labelling with CDH-8 antibodies co-localizes with pre (vGlut) and post synaptic (SynGAP) antigens in cortical neurons in culture. Figure 7C to F indicate CDH-8 immunogold labelling at asymmetrical glutamatergic synapses. The antibodies are subjected to some basic characterization but s the authors point out they lack the quantification to define is the labelling is predominantly pre or post synaptic.\n\n21/8/2017 Pim\n- membrane association inferred from TM domain.. Experimental description: Materials and methods:Figure 7 A and B contains cortical culture staining \"Cortical neurons were cultured from E 18.5 Sprague- Dawley Rats. In addition immunogold EM in Figure 7C-F is performed on sections of dorsal striatum \"sections through P30 mouse striatum were prepared for electron microscopy\".\n\n21/8/2017 Pim\n- Species selection based on EM pictures --> mouse" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3185-5709" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0755-5899" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-7351-8706" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0938-8534" ;
        dc:date           "2017-08-21" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_1065" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10090" .

